<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 16:09:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登还需要多少证据来证明内塔尼亚胡不是美国盟友？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/how-much-more-proof-does-biden-need-that-netanyahu-is-not-a-u-s-ally/00000190-30e8-d4fa-ad9d-ffe94ffa0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在这段令人翻白眼的视频中指责美国人扣押了一批军火，并再次让人想起了温斯顿·丘吉尔，这是他在玩弄政治——这是他唯一知道该怎么做的事情。他七月份在国会发表讲话的邀请应该推迟到美国大选之后</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/how-much-more-proof-does-biden-need-that-netanyahu-is-not-a-u-s-ally/00000190-30e8-d4fa-ad9d-ffe94ffa0000</guid></item><item><title>“许多犹太人表示，如果极右或极左赢得选举，他们将离开法国”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-19/ty-article-podcast/many-jews-say-theyll-leave-france-if-the-far-right-or-extreme-left-win-the-election/00000190-2fe3-dc02-a7d8-eff7030c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:21:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-19/ty-article-podcast/many-jews-say-theyll-leave-france-if-the-far-right-or-extreme-left-win-the-election/00000190-2fe3-dc02-a7d8-eff7030c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列表示计划建立一个替代红十字会的机构来探视巴勒斯坦囚犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-to-establish-alternative-to-red-cross-for-visits-to-palestinian-prisoners/00000190-30d3-d700-a7f0-bdf388410000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，红十字会已停止探视被关押在以色列的巴勒斯坦人。以色列没有提供替代机制的细节，但国土报了解到，一个选择是法官和外国外交官的访问。以色列民权组织称此举违反国际法</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-to-establish-alternative-to-red-cross-for-visits-to-palestinian-prisoners/00000190-30d3-d700-a7f0-bdf388410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯犹太运动员逆流而行：“我是融合的伟大证明”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-arab-jewish-athlete-swims-against-the-current-im-great-proof-of-integration/00000190-308c-d5f5-a5d6-f9ee0e120000</link><description>亚当·马拉纳 (Adam Maraana) 的父亲是穆斯林，母亲是犹太教徒，他将成为半个世纪以来第一位代表以色列参加奥运会的阿拉伯运动员。他说，在这个黑暗时期，他也能成为一名成功的“迷你大使”</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-arab-jewish-athlete-swims-against-the-current-im-great-proof-of-integration/00000190-308c-d5f5-a5d6-f9ee0e120000</guid></item><item><title>“不可能”：布鲁塞尔以加沙战争期间安全原因为由拒绝主办比利时与以色列的比赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-19/ty-article/impossible-brussels-declines-to-host-belgium-israel-match-citing-security-reasons/00000190-30c3-d5f5-a5d6-f9ebbe9b0000</link><description>该市最高体育官员表示，“很明显，宣布在首都举行这样一场比赛无疑会引发大规模示威活动。”布鲁塞尔甚至在加沙战争爆发之前就已处于安全戒备状态，比利时多次遭受极端主义袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-19/ty-article/impossible-brussels-declines-to-host-belgium-israel-match-citing-security-reasons/00000190-30c3-d5f5-a5d6-f9ebbe9b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列是否已成为加沙旁边的“利益区”，否认巴勒斯坦人的苦难？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/has-israel-become-a-zone-of-interest-next-to-gaza-in-denial-of-palestinian-suffering/00000190-3008-d700-a7f0-bdea2b3f0000</link><description>一张将以色列郁郁葱葱的向日葵田与加沙废墟并列的照片在网上疯传，人们将其与一部讲述奥斯威辛附近纳粹指挥官田园风光的奥斯卡获奖影片相比较。这场辩论提醒我们，图像不仅暗示什么，还隐藏什么</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/has-israel-become-a-zone-of-interest-next-to-gaza-in-denial-of-palestinian-suffering/00000190-3008-d700-a7f0-bdea2b3f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡攻击拜登政府后，美国取消了与以色列就伊朗问题进行的战略会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-nixes-strategic-talks-with-israel-on-iran-after-netanyahu-attacks-biden/00000190-30a8-d340-a1f8-38ac9f9f0000</link><description>一名以色列高级官员表示，内塔尼亚胡指责美国扣留以色列武器，这损害了数周来的协调努力；以色列总理此后收回了他的主张</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:01:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-nixes-strategic-talks-with-israel-on-iran-after-netanyahu-attacks-biden/00000190-30a8-d340-a1f8-38ac9f9f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考古学家一劳永逸地证明：人类对巨型动物的灭绝负有责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/israeli-scientists-show-definitively-humans-were-responsible-for-megafauna-extinction/00000190-2fbb-d700-a7f0-affbb2ef0000</link><description>特拉维夫大学的米基·本多尔和兰·巴尔凯并没有打算解决灭绝难题。但是在研究人类进化时，一具巨大的骷髅从我们的衣柜里突然出现</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 13:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/israeli-scientists-show-definitively-humans-were-responsible-for-megafauna-extinction/00000190-2fbb-d700-a7f0-affbb2ef0000</guid></item><item><title>不完全是圣殿：为什么以色列的犹太教堂如此没有吸引力？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-exactly-temples-why-are-israels-synagogues-so-unattractive/00000190-2b27-d340-a1f8-2b2725ec0000</link><description>虽然世界各地的犹太教堂都富丽堂皇，但以色列的情况却大不相同。做错了什么？</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 13:10:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-exactly-temples-why-are-israels-synagogues-so-unattractive/00000190-2b27-d340-a1f8-2b2725ec0000</guid></item><item><title>卫星图像显示黎巴嫩南部村庄遭到破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/satellite-images-show-devastation-in-the-villages-of-southern-lebanon/00000190-302d-d39e-a999-76ef9a070000</link><description>以色列对真主党火灾的反应已导致 10 万黎巴嫩人撤离。南部地区数千栋房屋被完全摧毁，损失达数十亿美元</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 12:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/satellite-images-show-devastation-in-the-villages-of-southern-lebanon/00000190-302d-d39e-a999-76ef9a070000</guid></item><item><title>“拉比法”危机表明内塔尼亚胡是多么容易受到极端正统派的勒索</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/crisis-over-rabbis-law-shows-how-vulnerable-netanyahu-is-to-extortion-by-ultra-orthodox/00000190-2f45-d340-a1f8-2f457d190000</link><description>在充满死亡和悲伤的时刻，内塔尼亚胡的联盟正在自杀，因为一项立法的目标是为极端正统政党创造大量就业机会。然而，几名“反叛”利库德集团议员代表了政党选民的强烈情绪，他们再也无法忍受恶心了</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 08:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/crisis-over-rabbis-law-shows-how-vulnerable-netanyahu-is-to-extortion-by-ultra-orthodox/00000190-2f45-d340-a1f8-2f457d190000</guid></item><item><title>ADL 因对以色列可靠性和反犹太主义的担忧而面临维基百科禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/adl-faces-wikipedia-ban-over-reliability-concerns-on-israel-antisemitism/00000190-2f1d-d2ff-a5d1-7fdf29a30000</link><description>一位编辑写道，“反诽谤联盟似乎不再遵守反犹太主义的严肃、主流和学术上令人信服的定义”，他要求讨论反犹太主义的请求最终导致了禁令的实施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 07:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/adl-faces-wikipedia-ban-over-reliability-concerns-on-israel-antisemitism/00000190-2f1d-d2ff-a5d1-7fdf29a30000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗敦促真主党削弱以色列的核能力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hurtling-toward-nuclear-capability-iran-urges-hezbollah-to-wear-israel-down/00000190-2cd5-d701-a3d2-7cff0e120000</link><description>以色列情报机构认为，德黑兰对加沙和黎巴嫩战争的进展感到满意，许多伊朗人将其视为击败以色列的长期计划的一部分。随着核能力变得越来越迫在眉睫，人们对内塔尼亚胡如何驾驭局势的担忧与日俱增</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hurtling-toward-nuclear-capability-iran-urges-hezbollah-to-wear-israel-down/00000190-2cd5-d701-a3d2-7cff0e120000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷寻求与哈马斯达成人质协议，美国对以色列与真主党的冲突感到担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-frets-over-israel-hezbollah-flare-up-as-jerusalem-seeks-hostage-deal-with-hamas/00000190-2d0e-d2de-af9e-6deed31c0000</link><description>美国高级官员警告以色列北部边境可能爆发全面战争，耶路撒冷表示，未能与哈马斯达成协议可能会加剧局势</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-frets-over-israel-hezbollah-flare-up-as-jerusalem-seeks-hostage-deal-with-hamas/00000190-2d0e-d2de-af9e-6deed31c0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉：如果以色列战事升级，入侵加利利已提上日程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-live/idf-ten-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-thousands-protest-govt-demand-gaza-deal/00000190-2e48-d39e-a999-7ece6e070000</link><description>以色列国防军：从黎巴嫩发射了 15 枚火箭弹，瞄准以色列北部 ■ 加沙消息来源称，以色列国防军坦克深入拉法 ■ 内塔尼亚胡批评拜登政府后，美国取消了与以色列就伊朗问题举行的战略会议 ■ 以色列国防军：从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 15 枚火箭弹 ■ 加沙消息来源称以色列坦克开进拉法西部 ■ 以色列国防军称从加沙发射的“空中目标”落在以色列领土的空地上</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 02:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-live/idf-ten-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-thousands-protest-govt-demand-gaza-deal/00000190-2e48-d39e-a999-7ece6e070000</guid></item><item><title>面对自己联盟的反对，内塔尼亚胡被迫废除具有分裂性的“拉比法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/facing-pushback-from-his-own-coalition-netanyahu-forced-to-pull-divisive-rabbis-law/00000190-2da9-d2de-af9e-6deb88460000</link><description>尽管以色列总理从关键小组中驱逐了两名流氓利库德集团成员，但仍无法为新立法赢得多数席位</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 23:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/facing-pushback-from-his-own-coalition-netanyahu-forced-to-pull-divisive-rabbis-law/00000190-2da9-d2de-af9e-6deb88460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察暴力在与特拉维夫篮球队的最新冲突中从政治蔓延到体育领域</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-violence-spills-from-politics-to-sports-in-latest-clashes-with-tel-aviv-team/00000190-2ca5-d701-a3d2-7caf987a0000</link><description>以色列警方与特拉维夫夏普尔队球迷之间爆发的冲突是警察部队与夏普尔队球迷之间长期紧张关系的一部分，而伊塔马尔·本-格维尔则加剧了这种关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-violence-spills-from-politics-to-sports-in-latest-clashes-with-tel-aviv-team/00000190-2ca5-d701-a3d2-7caf987a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女队在欧洲游泳锦标赛上夺得以色列首枚金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-team-wins-israels-first-ever-gold-in-european-swimming-championship/00000190-2bb1-d5f5-a5d6-ebfba4350000</link><description>以色列自由泳接力游泳运动员阿纳斯塔西娅·戈尔本科、达里亚·戈洛瓦蒂、阿亚拉·斯皮茨和莉亚·波隆斯基在欧洲游泳锦标赛上赢得以色列历史上第一枚金牌，男子团体获得第四名</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-team-wins-israels-first-ever-gold-in-european-swimming-championship/00000190-2bb1-d5f5-a5d6-ebfba4350000</guid></item><item><title>真主党播出无人机镜头，据称显示对以色列海法港和以色列国防军海军基地的监视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-airs-drone-footage-allegedly-showing-surveillance-of-haifa-port-idf-navy-base/00000190-2c03-d2ff-a5d1-7ccf791c0000</link><description>除了以色列海军在海法港口的主要基地外，真主党还声称拍摄了海法的安全设施；以色列外长威胁对真主党和黎巴嫩发动“全面”战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 18:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-airs-drone-footage-allegedly-showing-surveillance-of-haifa-port-idf-navy-base/00000190-2c03-d2ff-a5d1-7ccf791c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡攻击拜登：阻止向以色列运送武器是“不可思议的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-attacks-biden-inconceivable-to-hold-back-arms-shipments-to-israel/00000190-2c13-db38-adff-fcb344ab0000</link><description>当被问及这批武器运输的状况时，美国国务卿表示，这批重载炸弹仍在接受审查，但“其他一切进展正常”；白宫表示：“我们不知道他在说什么”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 17:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-attacks-biden-inconceivable-to-hold-back-arms-shipments-to-israel/00000190-2c13-db38-adff-fcb344ab0000</guid></item></channel></rss>